unchy creative sees a giant 3D hand reach from within the billboard, grab a Four'N Twenty pie, and take a bite.\", \"from\": 382, \"to\": 547, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The execution is part of Four'N Twenty's recently launched creative idea \\\"Being a Fan is Hungry Work\\\", which celebrates those who put sport first no matter what.\", \"from\": 548, \"to\": 709, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"It's incredible to be able to partner with such an iconic Australian brand like Four'N Twenty, push the boundaries of 3DOOH, and create a show-stopping execution on our newest screen in the heart of one of Australia's busiest retail precincts,\\\" said QMS chief sales officer, Tim Murphy.\", \"from\": 711, \"to\": 998, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 770, \"end\": 780, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australians\", \"score\": 0.990258740214617, \"rank\": 0.007614165131166826, \"text\": \"Australian\", \"types\": [\"Q41710\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australians\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australians\"}, {\"begin\": 918, \"end\": 927, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia\", \"score\": 0.9998323197492291, \"rank\": 0.00014900372891791857, \"text\": \"Australia\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia\"}, {\"begin\": 962, \"end\": 965, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Konica_Minolta\", \"score\": 0.9993792261888624, \"rank\": 0.0006211578705191471, \"text\": \"QMS\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Konica_Minolta\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Konica_Minolta\"}, {\"begin\": 987, \"end\": 997, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tim_Murphy_(American_politician)\", \"score\": 0.5478073799118423, \"rank\": 0.6587901701323685, \"text\": \"Tim Murphy\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\":